text: José Luis Calvo (born 28 March 1942) is a Spanish former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960, 1968, 1972 and the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Spain Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Soria
